latestPosts.caption: we’re celebrating one year of your favorite multipurpose color corrector, Hideaway 🧁 with a little treat from founder @wendezomnir ✨

if there’s one thing you should know about #Caliray founder @wendezomnir, it’s that she’s always moving—and looking good while doing it 🙂‍↕️

high performance, effortless style. that’s the Caliray way ✨

WendeZomnir, co-founder of UrbanDecay, shares how launching the brand in the 90s came with its own set of challenges. Back then, it was all about getting products made, but today, it’s about cutting through the noise in a crowded market. 💄✨

In this week’s Living Ageless & Bold episode, Wende and I dive into her story of how she grew her brand and got to where she is today with her new company Caliray.🎙️🌟

If she can do it, so can you. It’s never too late to build your own success! 💪
